import lasagne
import theano
import theano.tensor as T
import gensim
import collections
import time
import numpy as np
import h5py
import pickle
#from fuel.streams import ServerDataStream
from lasagne.regularization import regularize_layer_params_weighted, l2, l1
from lasagne.regularization import regularize_layer_params
from theano.ifelse import ifelse
from lasagne.layers import InputLayer
from lasagne.layers import DenseLayer
from lasagne.layers import BatchNormLayer
from lasagne.layers import NonlinearityLayer
from lasagne.layers import DropoutLayer
from lasagne.layers import Pool2DLayer as PoolLayer
from lasagne.layers import Conv2DLayer as ConvLayer
#from lasagne.layers.dnn import Conv2DDNNLayer as ConvLayer
from lasagne.nonlinearities import softmax
#import progressbar
from time import sleep
import csv
from lasagne.regularization import regularize_layer_params_weighted, l2, l1
from lasagne.regularization import regularize_layer_params
import random
from utils.models import build_vggmodel,build_vggpool5model,LSTMmodel,build_custom_mlp,load_dataset
from utils.validation import validation
def build_vggpool5model(input_var=None):
    net = {}
    net['input_layer'] = InputLayer((None, 512, 7, 7),input_var=input_var)
    net['fc6'] = DenseLayer(net['input_layer'], num_units=4096)
    net['fc6_batchnorm'] = BatchNormLayer(net['fc6'],axes='auto',epsilon=1e-4,alpha=0.1, beta=lasagne.init.Constant(0),gamma=lasagne.init.Constant(1), mean=lasagne.init.Constant(0), inv_std=lasagne.init.Constant(1))
    net['fc6_dropout'] = DropoutLayer(net['fc6_batchnorm'], p=0.5)
    net['fc7'] = DenseLayer(net['fc6_dropout'], num_units=4096)
    net['fc7_batchnorm'] = BatchNormLayer(net['fc7'],axes='auto',epsilon=1e-4,alpha=0.1, beta=lasagne.init.Constant(0),gamma=lasagne.init.Constant(1), mean=lasagne.init.Constant(0), inv_std=lasagne.init.Constant(1))
    net['fc7_dropout'] = DropoutLayer(net['fc7_batchnorm'], p=0.5)
    net['prob'] = DenseLayer(net['fc7_dropout'], num_units=300, nonlinearity=None)
    return net
